OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHosepipe ban set to come   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finto force                 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A hosepipe ban is set to come into     
OL,6, force in parts of southern England.    
OL,8,FThe move will be imposed on Southern   
OL,9,FWater customers in Hampshire and the   
OL,10,FIsle of Wight from 17:00 BST.          
OL,12,FThis means that using hosepipes to     
OL,13,Fwater gardens, clean cars, fill        
OL,14,Fornamental ponds and swimming pools    
OL,15,Fwill not be allowed.                   
OL,17,FThe restrictions are expected to last  
OL,18,Ffor three weeks. Similar measures are  
OL,19,Fbeing introduced across Kent and Surrey
OL,20,Fafter the driest July since 1935.      
